---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Resync Technology" description="About Resync Technology — engineering-led execution, automation-first systems, and clean architecture.">
  <section class="bg-paper text-ink">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm text-slateink shadow-soft">
          <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-resync-600"></span>
          About Resync Technology
        </p>

        <h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl font-black tracking-tight md:text-6xl">
          A small studio built for shipping.
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slateink/80">
          Resync Technology is an engineering-led software studio. We modernize systems, automate operations, and ship reliable products with clean architecture.
          We like small teams, tight feedback loops, and code you can maintain a year from now.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-xl2 border border-black/10 bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold">Engineering-led</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slateink/75">Clean systems, strong foundations, practical decisions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl2 border border-black/10 bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold">Automation-first</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slateink/75">Less manual work. More leverage. Repeatable workflows.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl2 border border-black/10 bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold">Reliable delivery</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slateink/75">Clear scope, predictable timelines, and production visibility.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-14 grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-xl2 border border-black/10 bg-white p-8 shadow-soft">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Why we exist</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-slateink/80 leading-relaxed">
            A lot of teams get stuck with tools that don’t fit, workflows that break, and apps that are hard to maintain.
            Resync exists to build software that actually supports operations — fast, clean, and built to last.
          </p>

          <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-slateink/80">
            <li>• Modern web apps and internal tools</li>
            <li>• iOS-first mobile development</li>
            <li>• API integrations and automation</li>
            <li>• Observability + monitoring</li>
            <li>• Technical consulting + architecture</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl2 border border-black/10 bg-white p-8 shadow-soft">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Featured project</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-slateink/80 leading-relaxed">
            <span class="font-semibold">Invoice Americano</span> — an iOS invoicing app built for contractors and small business owners.
            Create invoices quickly, keep client history organized, generate professional PDFs, and connect payments seamlessly.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-6 rounded-xl border border-black/10 bg-resync-50/60 p-5">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold">What it’s solving</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slateink/80">
              People need invoices that look professional, are easy to send, and are easy to track — without expensive tools or complicated workflows.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <span class="rounded-full bg-black/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-slateink">iOS</span>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-black/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-slateink">Payments</span>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-black/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-slateink">PDF Generation</span>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-black/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-slateink">Automation</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-14 rounded-xl2 border border-black/10 bg-white p-8 shadow-soft">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Work with us</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-slateink/80 leading-relaxed">
          If you want a fast, reliable build with clean architecture — tell us what you’re trying to accomplish.
          We’ll help you scope it and ship.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="/#contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl2 bg-resync-600 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-soft hover:bg-resync-700">
            Start a Project
          </a>
          <a href="/#work" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl2 border border-black/10 bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slateink hover:bg-black/5">
            View Work
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
